VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT org\.apache\.commons\.collections
WHEN EXPR MISSING:SerializationBinder|AllowType|ValidatingObjectInputStream|trusted && MISSING:test|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the usage of the Apache Commons Collections library, which has known vulnerabilities related to deserialization.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Insecure Package: org.apache.commons.collections.
